94-15-05 Boeing: 

Amendment 39-8976. Docket 94-NM-07-AD.



Applicability: All Model 747-400 series airplanes, certificated in any category. 
Compliance: Required as indicated, unless accomplished previously. 
To ensure the integrity of the fail safe features of the thrust reverser system, accomplish the following: 
(a) For Model 747-400 series airplanes powered by Pratt & Whitney PW4000 series engines: Accomplish paragraphs
(a)(1) and (a)(2) of this AD. 
(1) Within 90 days after the effective date of this AD, perform an inspection to detect damage to the bullnose seal on
