Step 4_determine DASTM gain or loss attributable to 
certain assets_

(A) 

General rule. 

The taxpayer shall determine 
the dollar amount of DASTM gain or loss attributable to assets in 
each group identified in paragraph (e)(3)(iii) of this section 
(Step 3) as follows: 


