SUMMARY: 

A special local regulation is being adopted for the marine event, Venetian Festival Yacht Parade. This event will
be held on Round Lake, Charlevoix, MI on July 23, 1994. The Venetian Festival Yacht Parade will have an estimated 25
power and sailboats, parading in a closed course on Round Lake which could pose hazards to navigation in the area. This
