Recordkeeping. 

OSHA has redesignated the logging of inspections and test requirements as paragraph (d) Recordkeeping. The changes
proposed to the requirements of previous paragraph (c) addressing logging of inspections and tests were contained
in paragraph (c) of the proposal. 
In paragraph (d)(1) OSHA has made substantive changes to the language of previous paragraph (c)(1). OSHA is requiring
